ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of HELEN M. GRAHAM of Toronto, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 27, 2003, in the place of Irene Szylinger, whose term will expire.
